*>CALL サブプログラムを呼び出す
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. GETTING_STARTED_30_CALL.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
DATA DIVISION.
    WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
        01 PRM.
            05 WK_DATE PIC X(21).
        01 PRM_1.
            05 WK_NUM PIC 99 VALUE ZERO.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    SUB_CALL SECTION.
        CALL "SUB_SAMPLE01KO".
    PASS_BY_VALUE.
        MOVE FUNCTION CURRENT-DATE TO WK_DATE.
        CALL "SUB_SAMPLE02KO" USING BY CONTENT PRM.
        DISPLAY "値渡し引き渡し元:"WK_DATE.
    PASS_BY_REFERENCE.
        DISPLAY "参照渡し引き渡し元:"WK_NUM.
        CALL "SUB_SAMPLE03KO" USING BY REFERENCE PRM_1.
        DISPLAY "引き渡して一を足した後:"WK_NUM.
    END_PROCEDURE.
        STOP RUN.
END PROGRAM GETTING_STARTED_30_CALL.

